```plantuml
@startuml IBMDeveloperMEA_YPDL-Recurrent-Neural-Networks-using-TensorFlow-Keras

actor User

participant JupyterNotebook as "Jupyter Notebook"
participant ScriptsReader as "scripts/reader.py"
participant TensorFlowKeras as "TensorFlow Keras"
participant LSTMModel as "LSTM Model"

User -> JupyterNotebook: Start Tutorial
JupyterNotebook -> ScriptsReader: Load Penn Treebank Dataset
ScriptsReader -> JupyterNotebook: Return Processed Data

JupyterNotebook -> TensorFlowKeras: Initialize LSTM Model
JupyterNotebook -> TensorFlowKeras: Add Embedding Layer
JupyterNotebook -> TensorFlowKeras: Add LSTM Layers
JupyterNotebook -> TensorFlowKeras: Add Dense Layer with Softmax

JupyterNotebook -> LSTMModel: Train Model with Data
LSTMModel -> JupyterNotebook: Return Trained Model

JupyterNotebook -> LSTMModel: Evaluate Model
LSTMModel -> JupyterNotebook: Return Evaluation Metrics

JupyterNotebook -> User: Display Metrics and Visualizations

@enduml
